{"tid":1402833,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先發夢係彌敦道前線叫人衝警犬既手足，我屌晒你地老母！","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T07:53:45.000Z","uid":255169,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbab715908e02251e24fca6a75bd1f803a04cad0","tid":1402833,"uid":255169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"我知你地好撚憎popo, 我都好想用麻包袋笠住張狗砌！但係請你地諗返頭先果個情況，我地衝得贏既機會有幾大？就算比你衝到，𡁻低左幾隻狗啦，你發洩完又得到啲咩？值唔值得因為一時之氣而令到成班手足比人拉？<br />\n<br />\n請你地記返起我地既目標係要對準政權，唔好再比仇恨蒙蔽你地既雙眼！做大事要好好控制自己既情緒，如果你控制唔到情緒既話，請你退落黎唔好做咪手！頭先你地咁做係陷我地成班手足於不義！已經差唔多比人拉左200個人啦，唔好再白白送頭！<br />\n求下你地理智少少啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8bb9ed54019bb1a640807aa0e7bf606be35061c5","tid":1402833,"uid":255169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd5934bc7a3d138e7c68e9dfc1c608bddf46836","tid":1402833,"uid":255169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a01fd6b45aa892f4f4cccb2429daecd9d50ed002","tid":1402833,"uid":255169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea07f094dce8e34d1cfea1117dca032a8c21f3b1","tid":1402833,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:26:12.000Z","msg":"有無問佢攞委任證？"},{"pid":"0e6bbd1fad17ce2b2e56238fef4b0dc72afc9111","tid":1402833,"uid":255169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"推到你地睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\"